description: There’s no better way to celebrate any Lakes Region occasion than with the refreshing selection of fun fruity flavors from Snowie!Come on out and spoon right into some Wild Cherry, Blue Raspberry, Piña Colada, and so much more. If you wanna keep the sweet but you’re counting calories, you can enjoy all of these flavors, sugar-free. For a refreshing and delightfully icy time, you gotta make your way straight to Snowie!
name: Lakes Region Snowie
